      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://herkimer.nygenweb.net/salisbury.html"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "New York State Routes 29 and 29A cross in the CDP, with 29A beginning right at the intersection.",
